<p style="text-align: left;">This site is working toward compiling an archive of all the world wide web's best free & open source Resources. Many of which exist unknown to the vast majority of users, simply because there is no profit in advertising such sites.<br/> <br/>Originally, I created a resource like this for my own private use but I wish now to develop it a bit more and make it available for all, hopefully all my visitors will benefit from these Wonderful website's services as I have.<br/><br/>These are just a few, check out the <a href="#links">Links Page</a> to see a full list of what I have gathered for our mutual benefit. Check back often as the list is added to regularly. Enjoy! <br/><br/>
